<p>The <code>@count</code> property returns the total number of items.</p>

<h2>Total Count</h2>
<pre>{open}users{close}
  {open}@first{close}Total users: {open}@count{close}{open}/@first{close}
{open}/users{close}</pre>

<p>Result:</p>
{users}
  {@first}Total users: {@count}{/@first}
{/users}

<h2>Progress Display</h2>
<pre>{open}colors{close}
  Processing {open}@current{close}/{open}@count{close}: {open}$colors{close}
{open}/colors{close}</pre>

<p>Result:</p>
<div>
{colors}
  Processing {@current}/{@count}: {$colors}<br>
{/colors}
</div>
